author: Costa Giannakopoulos
title: Costa Giannakopoulos
text: I'd honestly never heard of this online store until I couldn't find the parts I needed at my usual places. Glad I came across them though. Found the parts I needed, good prices, very fast shipping, and reliable tech support when I had a question. First but definitely not last time shopping here.
